--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 55fc01baa0be7b54e8ef6801bfc93ce6, type: 3}
  m_Name: YourselfTwo
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  PromptOneButtonDisplay: 0
  PromptTwoButtonDisplay: 0
  ButtonOneText: 
  ButtonTwoText: 
  NormalDialogue:
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: 'Just a curious question: Is your headache gone now?'
  - CharacterTitle: 3
    Message: No. It hurts worse.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: That's a shame.
  - CharacterTitle: 3
    Message: Uh huh.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: Well, not like shooting your head is the best medicine for a headache.
      I said that long before as an exaggeration to grab your attention.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: I know you understand that putting a bullet in your head wouldn't actually
      cure the physical pain, but you still did.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: And I know you realize that doing so would put you through more pain.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: The sensation of being shot is still very real before you're brought
      back to life, erasing all physical pain.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: You know, I saw you at the bar earlier, and you reached the threshold
      of six drinks per person.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: With drinking that much and shooting yourself, you're someone who enjoys
      pain.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: Addicted, sure, but it's not that simple.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: Pain is comforting because it's normalized for you.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: It feels right to punish yourself because of situations that made you
      feel like you deserve the pain.
  - CharacterTitle: 3
    Message: Are you sure we don't know each other? Because I don't like these repeated
      words.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: Currently, we don't know each other, but maybe in the past we did.
  - CharacterTitle: 3
    Message: Right...
  - CharacterTitle: 3
    Message: "I don't like this introspection, just so you know\u2026"
  - CharacterTitle: 3
    Message: I won't comment on what you said before, but others can't possibly understand
      that addiction for pain or outright refuse to understand.
  - CharacterTitle: 3
    Message: People judge. They judge based on the limited information they have
      of a person, the things that person has done, their interactions with others.
  - CharacterTitle: 3
    Message: People always judge. Some keep it to themselves, but it's still the
      same. People assume too. People are all the same.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: You belong to suffering.
  - CharacterTitle: 3
    Message: I belong to the system of suffering. I'm just a cog in a machine, even
      in this casino, to keep your revenue flowing...
  - CharacterTitle: 0
    Message: They pull more wool from their arm as the stinging sensation worsens.
  - CharacterTitle: 0
    Message: The creature takes the wool and moves it beneath the table.
  - CharacterTitle: 1
    Message: I'll start a new round.
  ButtonOneDialogue: []
  ButtonTwoDialogue: []
